/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後第二日晏就無啦啦問我: 你做咩今日無返工？<br />\n心諗請個陣咪同你講左邊幾日返得<br />\n又無更表，前一日收工又無叫我返<br />\n咁等人返工就請ft唔好請pt啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\non99，最後就無再叫我返工<br />\n淨係某日叫左我上去拎糧<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事後都有再用個app搵工<br />\n但send親cv都石沉大海<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\np.s.: 依家份工穩定又唔洗ot，都無on9阿頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1f7727264c2ea70b5c46e5e944d7effb85d282","tid":2513262,"uid":323791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4e5ffafc9a1fb1295fedcee8c25c7bfa35dbd41","tid":2513262,"uid":349103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"466a56731a15f547e45faa62b3ae52ac75844acc","tid":2513262,"uid":323791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:17:23.000Z","msg":"如題。<br />\n發現呢個app入面有好多伏工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係話講緊工作內容果d伏 <br />\n有冇人有經驗可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:30:16.000Z","msg":"一睇就知伏啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />on9先喺嗰度報 <br />\n不如正正經經去<strong><span class=\"red\">ig，JobDB</span></strong>等等搵仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:47:09.000Z","msg":"noted with thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8639f08eaeb32d85bb041e532f9e7802bcc8555","tid":2513262,"uid":66365,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4e5ffafc9a1fb1295fedcee8c25c7bfa35dbd41","tid":2513262,"uid":349103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote